Use of this code follows a "quid pro quo" principle:
If you use code from this project, you must give something back to the project.

This means that:

• Improvements or fixes should be contributed back to the RobUI project
  when possible (for example via pull requests).

• Any project using code from RobUI must clearly credit the RobUI project
  and its author.

• Reuse of code in other addons or projects requires permission from
  the author.

Permission to reuse code will generally be granted as long as proper
credit is given and the author has been contacted beforehand.

The following is NOT permitted without explicit permission:

• Redistributing this addon under a different name
• Publishing derivative addons based on this codebase
• Reusing substantial portions of the code without credit
• Distributing modified versions outside the official repository

All contributions to the RobUI project will be properly credited.

The author reserves the right to modify or change this license at any time
without prior notice.

